{% comment %}Shown when elaris-home has no faq_item blocks (e.g. static section without settings_data blocks).{% endcomment %}
<details class="accordion-item" name="faq-home-{{ home_section_id }}">
  <summary class="accordion-header">
    Can I use these products every day?
    <span class="icon">+</span>
  </summary>
  <div class="accordion-body">
    Yes. Floral Blossom Hair Mist is safe for daily use (even several times a day). Hair Regrowth Spray is designed for daily use, morning and night. Anti-Frizz Keratin Serum can be used daily or whenever your hair needs smoothness and control.
  </div>
</details>
<details class="accordion-item" name="faq-home-{{ home_section_id }}">
  <summary class="accordion-header">
    Will they leave my hair or scalp sticky or greasy?
    <span class="icon">+</span>
  </summary>
  <div class="accordion-body">
    No. The hair mist is made to feel fresh without stickiness. The keratin serum is non-greasy and does not weigh hair down. The regrowth spray absorbs quickly and is not meant to leave the scalp feeling greasy.
  </div>
</details>
<details class="accordion-item" name="faq-home-{{ home_section_id }}">
  <summary class="accordion-header">
    How do damp hair, dry hair, and heat styling work with these products?
    <span class="icon">+</span>
  </summary>
  <div class="accordion-body">
    The hair mist works best on dry hair for instant freshness and a long-lasting floral scent. The keratin serum works on both damp and dry hair and helps protect against heat from styling tools. The regrowth spray should stay on the scalp—overnight wear is ideal.
  </div>
</details>
<details class="accordion-item" name="faq-home-{{ home_section_id }}">
  <summary class="accordion-header">
    Do I need to rinse anything out?
    <span class="icon">+</span>
  </summary>
  <div class="accordion-body">
    Leave the regrowth spray on the scalp (no rinse; overnight works best). The mist and serum are leave-in style—apply and style as usual.
  </div>
</details>
<details class="accordion-item" name="faq-home-{{ home_section_id }}">
  <summary class="accordion-header">
    Are elaréhair hair products suitable for all hair types?
    <span class="icon">+</span>
  </summary>
  <div class="accordion-body">
    Yes. They suit different textures and needs—from frizz control and shine to support for thinning or weaker hair. Each product page has tailored FAQs if you want more detail.
  </div>
</details>
